classDiagram
    class Owner {
        +str name
        +list~Pet~ pets
        +add_pet()
        +remove_pet()
        +get_all_tasks()
    }

    class Pet {
        +str name
        +str species
        +float age_years
        +str notes
        +list~Task~ tasks
        +add_task()
        +remove_task()
        +get_pending_tasks()
    }

    class Task {
        +str title
        +str description
        +time scheduled_time
        +str frequency
        +bool completed
        +date due_date
        +update_task()
        +mark_complete()
        +reschedule()
        +is_due_on()
    }

    class Scheduler {
        +Owner owner
        +get_all_tasks()
        +get_pending_tasks()
        +filter_tasks(completed, pet_name)
        +sort_by_time(tasks)
        +organize_by_time(tasks)
        +find_conflicts(tasks)
        +get_conflict_warning(tasks)
        +_create_next_occurrence(task, plan_date)
        +complete_task(task, plan_date)
        +summarize()
    }

    note for Scheduler "Handles ordering, filtering, conflict detection, recurring-task progression, and readable summaries"

    Owner "1" --> "0..*" Pet : owns
    Pet "1" --> "0..*" Task : contains
    Scheduler --> Owner : manages
    Scheduler ..> Task : organizes
    Scheduler ..> Task : detects_conflicts_with
